                  "<p>One evening, after a long day at work, Jake approached Ethan’s office. “Can I talk to you for a minute?” he asked hesitantly.</p>",
                  "<p>“Of course, Jake. Come in,” Ethan replied, setting aside his work.</p>",
                  "<p>Jake took a deep breath. “I just wanted to thank you, Ethan. For everything. You didn’t have to help me, but you did. And I’m truly sorry for how I treated you in the past.”</p>",
                  "<p>Ethan smiled warmly. “Thank you, Jake. It takes a lot of courage to apologize and make amends. I’m proud of how far you’ve come.”</p>",
                  "<p>Jake nodded, visibly relieved. “I won’t let you down, Ethan. I promise.”</p>"
