            description: 'I believe in you, Arjun. But we need to be realistic.......',
            content: "<p>\"Against All Odds\" tells the gripping tale of Arjun and Maya, whose love defies the odds stacked against them. In modern-day India, Arjun, a determined young man with a modest background, falls deeply for Maya. However, Maya is trapped in an unhappy arranged marriage to a wealthy and influential man.</p><p>Despite facing immense challenges—opposition from their families, legal battles, and personal risks—Arjun and Maya refuse to give up on their love. Together, they navigate a tough journey, holding onto hope and each other. This Arjun and Mays's story, Hope you enjoy it.</p>",
