                  "<p>His wife replied, 'I'll speak loudly so she can hear me.'</p>",
                  "<p>The next morning, Andare and his wife went to the palace. When they arrived at the Queen's chamber, the Queen smiled at Andare's wife and greeted her very loudly. Andare's wife, thinking the Queen couldn't hear, greeted her back just as loudly. They both started talking so loudly that everyone around them had to cover their ears because the noise was too much.</p>",
