              "<p>With Rachel and her family safely under protection, Alex and Harris returned to the precinct. They reviewed the evidence once more, looking for any clues they might have missed. \"There has to be someone else pulling the strings,\" Alex mused. \"Harlow had too much confidence. He wasn’t working alone.\"</p>",
