        "<p>Back home, Sarah helped Anya with her makeover. They experimented with makeup, enhancing her natural features without overshadowing them. For the first time, Anya saw herself in a new light. She wasn't just the quiet girl who loved books and art; she was someone with grace and beauty.</p>",
