        "<p>“You too, Emma,” he replied, watching as she left.</p>",
        "<p>For the first time, Alex felt a glimmer of hope. Maybe, just maybe, he could bridge the gap between their worlds.</p>",
        "<p>In the following days, Alex made a point to greet Emma whenever he saw her. Their conversations grew longer, their connection deeper. Alex’s feelings for her blossomed, and he found himself thinking about her constantly.</p>",
        "<p>One evening, as Alex was working on his homework, his mother entered the room.</p>",
        "<p>“You’ve been smiling a lot lately,” she remarked, a knowing look in her eyes.</p>",
