  content: "Tenali Rama is historic personality known for his wit and humor. He was a poet at the court of Krishnadevaraya, a 16th-century monarch of the Vijayanagara Empire in South India. Folktales about Tenali Rama spread far and wide. Today, he is considered one of the most beloved characters in Indian history.",
